==> 1038 <==
From Setzer.Woodrow@epamail.epa.gov  Tue Jul 31 17:47:13 2001
Received: from stat.math.ethz.ch (daemon@hypatia.ethz.ch [129.132.58.23])
	by pubhealth.ku.dk (8.9.3/8.9.1) with ESMTP id RAA10358
